  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK814">
<l>amarakat tāṟṟaṟukkuṅ kallāmā vaṉṉār </l>
<l>tamariṟ ṟaṉimai talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Solitude is more to be desired than the society of those who resemble the untrained horses which throw down (their riders) in the fields of battle.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
